query:
SELECT id as "id!: Uuid",
                      plan_name,
                      max_workspaces,
                      max_teams,
                      max_projects,
                      max_members,
                      max_storage_gb,
                      max_ai_requests_per_month,
                      created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                      updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
               FROM plan_limits
               ORDER BY
                   CASE plan_name
                       WHEN 'hobby' THEN 1
                       WHEN 'starter' THEN 2
                       WHEN 'pro' THEN 3
                       ELSE 4
                   END
